name: Night of the Stregha
description:
In a remote graveyard, what appears to be a coven composed by three witches of different ages is, in truth, the gathering of a single witch's soul in three different times of her life. Some say she possess a Silver Key, allowing her to access forgotten layers of the minds, from others, and her own.

764 X 1080 mp4 w/ sound
Stregha means "witch" in Italian

Original character design, sketch, drawing, digital painting / illustration and animation by Zamahel
